data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning three-bedroom, two-bathroom pool home with a den and spa is located in the desirable community of Lehigh Acres. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by an open-concept living area with plenty of natural light and soaring ceilings. The spacious kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining. The master suite is a true oasis, with a large bedroom, walk-in closet, and luxurious en suite bathroom with dual sinks, and a walk-in shower. The two additional bedrooms are spacious and comfortable, with easy access to the second full bathroom. The den provides a versatile space that can be used as a home office, media room, or additional bedroom. But the real showstopper of this home is the outdoor living area - step outside and you'll find a sparkling pool and spa, perfect for relaxing and entertaining on warm Florida days. The screened lanai provides ample space for entertaining. Located in the heart of Lehigh Acres, this home is just a short drive from shopping, dining, and entertainment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning property your own!
